#!/usr/bin/env python3
#MISE description="Regenerate pog-config.json.template from this script's source-of-truth dicts."
"""Source of truth for the BDSS ore distribution. Generates pog-config.json.template.

Edit the dicts below to tune ore distribution, then run `mise run genconfig` (or
just invoke this file directly — mise discovers it as a task via its shebang).

Each base ore is expanded into 5 variants (V1 shallowest/smallest, V5 deepest/largest)
with multiplicative parameter spread. Each planet picks a subset of variants per ore
based on its character, with the existing per-planet `p` budget split across the
chosen variants using a shallow-biased ratio.
"""

